OL,3,CBody of 'Green Boots' climber on
OL,4,CEverest for 30 years to be brought home
OL,6,FWarning: This article contains
OL,7,Fdistressing images.
OL,9,FIndian authorities are seeking to
OL,10,Fretrieve the body of a climber known
OL,11,Fas 'Green Boots' who has been at the
OL,12,Ftop of Mount Everest near the so-
OL,13,Fcalled 'death zone' for 30 years.
OL,15,FThe climber is believed to be either
OL,16,FTsewang Paljor or Lance Naik Dorje
OL,17,FMorup, who were both members of a six-
OL,18,Fperson Indo-Tibetan Border Police
OL,19,F(ITBP) team that became caught in a
OL,20,Fblizzard during an expedition in 1996.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
