OL,3,CBody of 'Green Boots' climber on
OL,4,CEverest for 30 years to be brought home
OL,6,FThree of the team turned back, but
OL,7,FPaljor, Morup, and one other named
OL,8,FSubedar Tsewang Smanla decided to try
OL,9,Fand summit. None of them returned.
OL,11,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
