OL,3,CBody of 'Green Boots' climber on
OL,4,CEverest for 30 years to be brought home
OL,6,FSince then. the body of Green Boots -
OL,7,Fone of 200 corpses believed to be on
OL,8,FEverest - remains at around 27,700ft
OL,9,Fon the mountain's northern slope
OL,10,Ffacing Tibet, with climbers forced to
OL,11,Fstep around him as part of their
OL,12,Fascent.
OL,14,FA group of Chinese mountaineers
OL,15,Fmanaged to pull the body further under
OL,16,Fa boulder in 2014 so it was less
OL,17,Fvisible.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
