OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781569069
OL,3,CBody of 'Green Boots' climber on
OL,4,CEverest for 30 years to be brought home
OL,6,FThe ITBP has now floated a tender to
OL,7,Fhire a high-altitude recovery agency
OL,8,Fto try and retrieve the body, Indian
OL,9,Fnewspaper The Tribune reports.
OL,11,FThe proposed operation would
OL,12,Freportedly require at least six
OL,13,Fsherpas, who would climb 8,000 metres
OL,14,Fto retrieve the body and bring it down
OL,15,Fthe mountain, before repatriating the
OL,16,Fremains to India.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
