CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781569069
OL,3,CBody of 'Green Boots' climber on
OL,4,CEverest for 30 years to be brought home
OL,6,FIt was reported that the ITBP hopes to
OL,7,Fcomplete the mission between June and
OL,8,FSeptember 2026, and it will be
OL,9,Fconducted in line with religious and
OL,10,Fcultural protocols.
OL,12,FThe tender document is said to
OL,13,Fidentify Green Boots as Morup.
OL,15,F'Green Boots' is not the only body
OL,16,FEverest climbers might see as they
OL,17,Fmake their ascent, with the body of
OL,18,FFrancys Arsentiev, known as 'Sleeping
OL,19,FBeauty', visible until she was moved
OL,20,Fout of view in 2007.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
