OL,3,CBody of 'Green Boots' climber on
OL,4,CEverest for 30 years to be brought home
OL,6,FArsentiev, who was the first American
OL,7,Fwoman to summit Mount Everest without
OL,8,Fbottled oxygen, died aged 40 in 1998.
OL,10,FThe top portion of Everest, above
OL,11,F26,000 feet, is commonly known as the
OL,12,F'death zone', and also features an
OL,13,Farea nicknamed 'Rainbow Valley' due to
OL,14,Fthe many multi-coloured jackets of the
OL,15,Fbodies within it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
